hive.today/20200306005842/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/wes-andersons-grand-budapest-hotel-672783 |archive-date=2020-03-06 |access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>，之後於2月27日在[[紐約|紐約]]的{{tsl|en|Film at Lincoln Center|林肯中心電影協會}}作北美首映<ref name="Specialty">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-preview-grand-budapest-hotel-grand-piano-journey-to-the-west-695053/ |title=Specialty B.O. Preview: 'The Grand Budapest Hotel', 'Grand Piano', 'Journey To The West: Conquering The Demons', 'Miele', 'Particle Fever', 'Bethlehem' |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-03-06 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306020702/https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-preview-grand-budapest-hotel-grand-piano-journey-to-the-west-695053/ |archive-date=2020-03-06 |access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>。

福斯探照燈影業帶頭開展了營銷活動。他們的策略包括發行商品、全球巡迴宣傳<ref name="varietypromo">{{Cite news |last=Stewart |first=Andrew |url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/five-keys-to-wes-andersons-hotel-success-story-1201154272/ |title=Wes Anderson's 'Grand Budapest Hotel': 5 Ways Marketing Was Key |date=2014-04-10 |work=Variety |access-date=2020-03-05 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306014358/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/five-keys-to-wes-andersons-hotel-success-story-1201154272/ |archive-date=2020-03-06}}</ref>、建立有關祖部羅卡文化的模擬網站<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.luerzersarchive.com/en/features/campaigns/grand-budapest-hotels-rolls-out-quirky-content-562.html |title=Grand Budapest Hotel's rolls out quirky content |last=Staff |website=Lürzer's Archive |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306014731/https://www.luerzersarchive.com/en/features/campaigns/grand-budapest-hotels-rolls-out-quirky-content-562.html |archive-date=2020-03-06}}</ref>和強調演員身上明星效應的預告<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2013/10/hot-trailer-grand-budapest-hotel-wes-anderso-video-613952/ |title=Hot Trailer: 'The Grand Budapest Hotel' |last=Staff |date=2013-10-17 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306020012/https://deadline.com/2013/10/hot-trailer-grand-budapest-hotel-wes-anderso-video-613952/ |archive-date=2020-03-06}}</ref>。他們其中一項最重要的營銷策略是講解影片，其詳細描述了製作與曼德糕餅店製品相同的甜品，並將粉絲提交給製片人的影片用於烹飪聯播網的電視商業廣告上<ref name=varietypromo />。[[普拉達|普拉達]]在柏林旗艦店店內陳列了與安德森聯手的定製行李箱系列<ref>{{Cite news |last=Vivarelli |first=Nick |url=https://variety.com/2014/film/festivals/wes-anderson-grand-budapest-hotel-prada-1201091474/ |title=Prada Celebrates Wes Anderson 'Grand' Collaboration With Berlin Display |date=2014-02-07 |work=Variety |access-date=2020-03-05 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306022411/https://variety.com/2014/film/festivals/wes-anderson-grand-budapest-hotel-prada-1201091474/ |archive-date=2020-03-06}}</ref>。

《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》於2014年2月26日在法國上映，隨之在全球推出。全面放映在第二週擴展至德國、比利時、英國、美國（3月7日）和其他兩個國際市場<ref name="France">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-frozen-crossing-1-billion-worldwide-692038/ |title=Update: International Box Office: 'The Hobbit: The Desolation Of Smaug' Has No. 1 Japan Opening; 'Lego' Builds to $121M Overseas; 'Frozen' Crossing $1B Worldwide; 'Robocop' Takes $20.5M In China; More |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2014-03-03 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306025354/https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-frozen-crossing-1-billion-worldwide-692038/ |archive-date=2020-03-06 |access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在美國開場時維持長達一個月的有限上映，並起初在紐約和洛杉磯的4間藝術影院放映<ref name=Specialty />。在[[第87屆奧斯卡金像獎|第87屆奧斯卡金像獎]]提名名單宣佈後，福斯在多個城市以短暫的重新上映廣告來重新增加電影在影院的存在感<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2015/01/grand-budapest-hotel-rerelease-oscars-1201351608/ |title='Grand Budapest Hotel' Checks Back Into Theaters After Oscar Nom Haul |last=Hipes |first=Patrick |date=2015-01-16 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200316162048/https://deadline.com/2015/01/grand-budapest-hotel-rerelease-oscars-1201351608/ |archive-date=2020-03-16 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref>。

=== 家用媒體 ===
福斯探照燈影業於2014年6月17日以[[DVD|DVD]]和[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]的形式重新發行<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=13820 |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel Blu-ray |date=2014-04-25 |website=Blu-ray.com |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202071616/http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=13820 |archive-date=2018-02-02 |access-date=2014-04-30}}</ref>。光碟中包括-{zh-hans:莫瑞;zh-hk:梅利;zh-tw:莫瑞;}-鏡頭的幕後花絮、宣傳片段、刪去鏡頭和影院預告片<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.slantmagazine.com/dvd/the-grand-budapest-hotel/ |title=Blu-ray Review: The Grand Budapest Hotel |last=Bowen |first=Chuck |date=2014-06-18 |website=[[偏鋒雜誌|Slant Magazine]] |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306040834/https://www.slantmagazine.com/dvd/the-grand-budapest-hotel/ |archive-date=2020-03-06 |access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在美國DVD和藍光光碟的首週銷量是有史以來第四高的電影，總共賣出92,196張賺得160萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.the-numbers.com/home-market/packaged-media-sales-chart/2014/06/22 |title=United States Combined DVD and Blu-ray Sales Chart for Week Ending June 22, 2014 |date=2014-06-22 |website=The Numbers |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306035932/https://www.the-numbers.com/home-market/packaged-media-sales-chart/2014/06/22 |archive-date=2020-03-06 |access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>。截止2015年3月，電影已賣出551,639張光碟<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Grand-Budapest-Hotel-The#tab=video-sales |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel – Video Sales |website=The Numbers |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200306040322/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Grand-Budapest-Hotel-The%23tab=video-sales |archive-date=2020-03-06 |access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>。

[[標準收藏|標準收藏]]經導演許可於2020年4月28日發行《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》特別版藍光光碟和DVD。光碟包括安德森、-{zh-cn:高布伦; zh-tw:高布倫; zh-hk:高拔林;}-、製作人{{tsl|en|Roman Coppola|羅曼·柯波拉}}和影評人肯特·瓊斯（{{lang|en|Kent Jones}}）的副音軌、故事板動畫、幕後花絮紀錄片、視頻文章以及全體新演員和工作人員的訪問<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.criterion.com/films/29601-the-grand-budapest-hotel |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel |website=[[標準收藏|The Criterion Collection]] |access-date=2020-01-17 |archive-date=2020-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200912160544/https://www.criterion.com/films/29601-the-grand-budapest-hotel |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 反應 ==
=== 票房 ===
《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》被認為是意想不到的票房成功<ref name="labox">{{Cite web |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-mn-wes-anderson-grand-budapest-hotel-box-office-20140323-story.html |title=Wes Anderson's 'Grand Budapest Hotel' builds at the box office |last=Olsen |first=Mark |date=2014-03-23 |website=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Media |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200313085641/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-mn-wes-anderson-grand-budapest-hotel-box-office-20140323-story.html |archive-date=2020-03-13 |access-date=2020-03-13}}</ref>。這部電影在北美強勁的開局後表現穩定，但在完成院線上映後成為安德森市場上最高票房的電影<ref name=guardgross /><ref name="Deadbox3">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2015/01/the-grand-budapest-hotel-ps-1201345744/ |title='The Grand Budapest Hotel' Tops Specialty B.O.'s Top 10 For 2014 |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2015-01-09 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200313091133/https://deadline.com/2015/01/the-grand-budapest-hotel-ps-1201345744/ |archive-date=2020-03-13 |access-date=2020-03-13}}</ref>。它在主要的歐洲和亞洲市場表現最為出色<ref name="guardgross">{{Cite news |last=Beaumont-Thomas |first=Ben |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/apr/16/the-grand-budapest-hotel-wes-anderson-highest-grossing |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel becomes Wes Anderson's highest-grossing film |date=2014-04-16 |work=The Guardian |access-date=2020-03-12 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200313041154/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/apr/16/the-grand-budapest-hotel-wes-anderson-highest-grossing |archive-date=2020-03-13 |publisher=Guardian Media Group}}</ref><ref name=wrapgross />。德國是獲利最豐厚的市場，而電影與該國的聯繫正正提高了票房表現<ref name=wrapgross />。南韓、澳洲、西班牙、法國和英國貢獻了電影部分的最高收入<ref name="wrapgross">{{Cite news |last=Cunningham |first=Todd |url=https://www.thewrap.com/grand-budapest-hotel-clicks-box-office-germany-shot/ |title='Grand Budapest Hotel' Clicks at Box Office in Germany, Where It Was Filmed |date=2014-04-04 |work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |access-date=2020-03-13 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200314030237/https://www.thewrap.com/grand-budapest-hotel-clicks-box-office-germany-shot/ |archive-date=2020-03-14}}</ref>。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在美國及加拿大地區共累積了5,930萬美元的票房（佔收入的34.3%），加上來自其他地區的1億1,360萬美元（65.7%），全球票房共計1億7,290萬美元<ref name="BOM" />，為2014年票房第46高的電影<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/world/2014/ |title=2014 Worldwide Box Office |website=Box Office Mojo |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200313035859/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/world/2014/ |archive-date=2020-03-13 |access-date=2020-03-12}}</ref>，而且是安德森目前為止最高票房的電影<ref>{{Cite news |last=Khatchatourian |first=Maane |url=https://variety.com/2014/film/box-office/grand-budapest-hotel-hits-100-mil-becomes-wes-andersons-highest-grossing-pic-1201157267/ |title='Grand Budapest Hotel' Hits $100 Mil, Becomes Wes Anderson's Highest-Grossing Pic |date=2014-04-14 |work=Variety |access-date=2020-03-13 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200313092656/https://variety.com/2014/film/box-office/grand-budapest-hotel-hits-100-mil-becomes-wes-andersons-highest-grossing-pic-1201157267/ |archive-date=2020-03-13}}</ref>。

電影在法國上映首週從172家影院收穫280萬美元，票房排在《{{tsl|en|Supercondriaque|臆想成病}}》和《[[直航殺機|-{zh-cn:空中营救;zh-tw:空中救援;zh-hk:直航殺機;}-]]》之後。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在巴黎的放映場數為首週週末最多<ref name=France />。這部電影的平均影院票房為16,220美元，是目前為止安德森執導作品中在法國最好的開場成績<ref name=Specialty />。在第二週，上映的影院增至192家，《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在法國取得另外的164萬美元票房<ref name=Deadbox4 />。下個週末的收入僅下降30%，總數為110萬美元<ref name="Deadbox5">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-need-for-speed-revs-up-45-6m-rise-of-an-empire-adds-41-3m-for-158m-overseas-cume-frozen-has-big-japan-opening-will-it-beat-toy-story-3-for-all-time-animation-record-699919/ |title=Update: Intl Box Office: 'Rise Of An Empire' Cumes $159.6M; Universal's Spanish Comedy Breaks Records; 'Need For Speed' China Haul Outpaces Domestic; 'Frozen' Hot In Japan; More |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2014-03-17 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200314051942/https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-need-for-speed-revs-up-45-6m-rise-of-an-empire-adds-41-3m-for-158m-overseas-cume-frozen-has-big-japan-opening-will-it-beat-toy-story-3-for-all-time-animation-record-699919/ |archive-date=2020-03-14 |access-date=2020-03-13}}</ref>。票房到3月24日增長了5%，《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在法國上映時總共收穫820萬美元<ref name=Deadbox6 />。

《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在3月6日該週從全球727家影院收穫620萬美元，收入最高的國家是比利時（從12家影院收穫156,000美元）、奧地利（從29家影院收穫162,000美元）、德國（從163家影院收穫153萬美元）和英國（從284家影院收穫153萬英鎊或185萬美元，為前三名首映成績）<ref name="Deadbox4">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-300-rise-of-an-empire-seeks-world-domination-opens-no-1-in-france-12-years-looking-at-oscar-bump-695156/ |title=Update: Intl Box Office: '300: Rise Of An Empire' Lifts To $88.8M; 'Non-Stop' Passes $100M Worldwide; More |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date= 2014-03-10 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200314044921/https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-300-rise-of-an-empire-seeks-world-domination-opens-no-1-in-france-12-years-looking-at-oscar-bump-695156/ |archive-date=2020-03-14 |access-date=2020-03-13}}</ref><ref name=guardgross2 />。下週，它在德國票房上升11%，並收穫110萬美元<ref name=Deadbox5 />。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》截止3月31日該週從德國影院取得520萬美元<ref name=Deadbox7 />。在英國全面放映的第二週憑藉不斷擴大的影院存在感提高了票房，而保持票房勢頭。到了第三週，電影從458家影院收穫127萬英鎊（155萬美元）名列國家票房前十高，並受到影評人好評<ref name="guardgross2">{{Cite news |last=Grant |first=Charles |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/mar/26/grand-budapest-hotel-top-spot-box-office |title=Grand Budapest Hotel overtakes Need for Speed to cruise into top spot |date=2014-03-26 |work=The Guardian |access-date=2020-03-13 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140327021442/http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/mar/26/grand-budapest-hotel-top-spot-box-office |archive-date=2014-03-27 |publisher=Guardian Media Group}}</ref>。一個月後，它在英國獲得1,320萬美元<ref name=Deadbox7 />。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》持續擴展至其他海外市場直到3月底，較為顯著成功的上映在瑞典（以498,108美元為票房冠軍）、西班牙（以100萬為票房第三）和南韓（全國有史以來最大型特製電影開場，從162家影院收穫622,109美元）<ref name="Deadbox6">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-noah-reigns-in-korea-with-1-1m-debut-biggest-opening-of-2014-702264/ |title=Update: Intl Box Office: 'Need For Speed' Adds $29.2M For No. 1; 'Noah' Reigns In Mexico & Korea With $14M; 'Peabody & Sherman' Crosses $100M; 'Spanish Affairs' Muy Caliente; Asian Pics Advance; More |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2014-03-24 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200314054910/https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-noah-reigns-in-korea-with-1-1m-debut-biggest-opening-of-2014-702264/ |archive-date=2020-03-14 |access-date=2020-03-14}}</ref>。在南韓上映的第二週，票房激增70%，達到996,000美元<ref name="Deadbox7">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-noah-shipshape-in-australia-russia-openings-overseas-cume-at-22m-from-4-markets-through-thursday-705857/ |title=Update: Intl Box Office: 'Captain America: The Winter Soldier' Captures $75.2M; 'Noah' Swells To $51.5M Cume; 'Rio 2' Breaks Brazil Records; 'Lego' Passes $400M; More |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2014-03-31 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200314060249/https://deadline.com/2014/03/international-box-office-noah-shipshape-in-australia-russia-openings-overseas-cume-at-22m-from-4-markets-through-thursday-705857/ |archive-date=2020-03-14 |access-date=2020-03-14}}</ref>。在其他地方的開場週末，《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在澳洲獲得180萬美元、在巴西獲得382,000美元和在義大利獲得100萬美元<ref name="Deadbox8">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/04/intl-box-office-rio-2-soars-with-63-4m-weekend-captain-america-the-winter-soldier-blasts-past-300m-overseas-noah-adds-36-2m-divergent-nears-50m-714141/ |title=Update: Intl Box Office: 'Rio 2' Soars With $63.4M; 'Captain America: The Winter Soldier' Blasts Past $300M Overseas; 'Noah' Adds $36.2M; 'Divergent' Nearing $50M |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2014-04-14 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200314062533/https://deadline.com/2014/04/intl-box-office-rio-2-soars-with-63-4m-weekend-captain-america-the-winter-soldier-blasts-past-300m-overseas-noah-adds-36-2m-divergent-nears-50m-714141/ |archive-date=2020-03-14 |access-date=2020-03-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/07/international-box-office-maleficent-frozen-transformers-extinction-dragon-tammy-edge-tomorrow-799879/ |title=Update: Intl Box Office: 'Transformers' Adds $52M In China Weekend; 'Dragon 2' Fires Up $30M; And How's 'Tammy'?; 'Maleficent' Dethrones 'Frozen' In Japan; More |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2014-07-08 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140816232934/http://deadline.com/2014/07/international-box-office-maleficent-frozen-transformers-extinction-dragon-tammy-edge-tomorrow-799879/ |archive-date=2014-08-16 |access-date=2020-03-14}}</ref>。這部電影於5月27日在全球票房超過1億美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/05/intl-box-office-x-men-bows-to-biggest-fox-opener-ever-godzilla-second-weekend-pushes-wb-to-1b-2014-blended-rolls-out-slowly-neighbors-continues-partying-735810/ |title=Update: Intl Box Office: Fan-Tastic 'X-Men' Bows To Biggest Fox Opener Ever And No. 1 In Every Market; 'Godzilla' Second Weekend Pushes WB To $1B 2014; 'Blended' Rolls Out Slowly; 'Neighbors' Still Partying, More |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2014-05-27 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20141210093558/http://deadline.com/2014/05/intl-box-office-x-men-bows-to-biggest-fox-opener-ever-godzilla-second-weekend-pushes-wb-to-1b-2014-blended-rolls-out-slowly-neighbors-continues-partying-735810/ |archive-date=2014-12-10 |access-date=2020-03-14}}</ref>。

《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在美國開場的4家影院總共獲得811,166美元，平均202,792美元，打破[[保羅·湯瑪斯·安德森|-{zh-cn:保罗·托马斯·安德森;zh-hk:保羅·湯馬士·安德遜;zh-tw:保羅·湯瑪斯·安德森;}-]]的《[[大师_(电影)|-{zh-hk:大師;zh-cn:大师;zh-tw:世紀教主;}-]]》成為最賺錢的有限上映真人電影紀錄<ref name="ptagross">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/grand-budapest-hotel-box-office-debut-record-696110/ |title=Box Office: 'Grand Budapest Hotel' Checks In With Record Per-Screen Average |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-03-09 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200314154750/https://deadline.com/2014/03/grand-budapest-hotel-box-office-debut-record-696110/ |archive-date=2020-03-14 |access-date=2020-03-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-300-rise-of-an-empire-commands-40m-mr-peabody-chases-in-30m-son-of-god-may-fall-55-or-more-in-second-weekend-695863/ |title=Box Office Final: '300: Rise Of An Empire' Commands $45M; 'Mr. Peabody' Chases In $32.2M; 'Son Of God' Falls 59% In Second Weekend, 'Budapest Hotel' Per Screen Stuns With Over $202K |last=Busch |first=Anita |date=2014-03-10 |website=Deadline |access-date=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2018-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181010130203/https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-300-rise-of-an-empire-commands-40m-mr-peabody-chases-in-30m-son-of-god-may-fall-55-or-more-in-second-weekend-695863/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。週末收益超過了福斯的期望，是迄今為止安德森執導作品中在美國最好開場<ref name=ptagross />。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》還超過《-{zh-tw:月昇冒險王國;zh-hk:小學雞私奔記;zh-hans:月升王国;}-》平均影院130,749美元的成績，是安德森目前為止最高有限上映開場的票房<ref name=ptagross />。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》對電影透過奧斯卡金像獎的威望來賺錢不再感興趣，而轉為吸引年輕和不常看電影的人，因而成為電影早期票房成功的關鍵<ref name=ptagross />。電影在有限上映中增加大型郊區多廳影院來保持票房勢頭，讓第二週的收入為360萬美元，並讓隨之而來的週末取得670萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-wes-anderson-grand-budapest-hotel-bad-words-le-week-end-699948/ |title=Specialty Box Office: 'Grand Budapest Hotel' Checks In With Lofty $55K PTA In Expansion; Bateman's 'Bad Words' Solid |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-03-16 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200316150333/https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-wes-anderson-grand-budapest-hotel-bad-words-le-week-end-699948/ |archive-date=2020-03-16 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/specialty-box-office-grand-budapest-hotel-nymphomaniac-cheap-thrills-enemy-703145/ |title=Specialty Box Office: 'Grand Budapest' Extends Reign In Expansion; 'Nymphomaniac' Bows So-So Theatrically |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-03-23 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200316150856/https://deadline.com/2014/03/specialty-box-office-grand-budapest-hotel-nymphomaniac-cheap-thrills-enemy-703145/ |archive-date=2020-03-16 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref>。這部電影於3月30日該週在北美977家影院上映，正式進入全面放映<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-the-raid-2-grand-budapest-hotel-cesar-chavez-706680/ |title=Specialty Box Office: 'Raid 2', 'Finding Vivian Maier' Start Solid, 'Cesar Chavez' Posts Middling Results |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-03-30 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200316153606/https://deadline.com/2014/03/box-office-the-raid-2-grand-budapest-hotel-cesar-chavez-706680/ |archive-date=2020-03-16 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref>。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》最成功的北美城市是紐約、洛杉磯、多倫多、華盛頓和蒙特利尔<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/04/box-office-scarlett-johansson-under-the-skin-dom-hemingway-710376/ |title=Specialty Box Office: Scarlett Johansson Reigns With Sci-Fier 'Under The Skin' |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-04-06 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200316153844/https://deadline.com/2014/04/box-office-scarlett-johansson-under-the-skin-dom-hemingway-710376/ |archive-date=2020-03-16 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref>。它的上映影院在4月中旬以1,467家達到巔峰，之後逐漸下降<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/04/specialty-box-office-results-fading-gigolo-717230/ |title=Specialty Box Office: 'Fading Gigolo' Seduces In Limited Opening; 'Under The Skin' Passes $1M |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-04-20 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200316154635/https://deadline.com/2014/04/specialty-box-office-results-fading-gigolo-717230/ |archive-date=2020-03-16 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref>。到4月底，電影國內收入超過5千萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/05/specialty-box-office-belle-ida-walk-of-shame-723875/ |title=Specialty Box Office: 'Belle' Is A Potent Lady; 'Ida' Shows Traction; 'Walk Of Shame' Tiptoes Into Limited Release |last=Brooks |first=Brian |date=2014-05-04 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200316155226/https://deadline.com/2014/05/specialty-box-office-belle-ida-walk-of-shame-723875/ |archive-date=2020-03-16 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref>。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》於2015年2月26日結束在北美的上映<ref>{{Cite web |url= https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl475497985/?ref_=bo_tt_gr_1 |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel |website=Box Office Mojo |dead-url=no|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200518011959/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl475497985/?ref_=bo_tt_gr_1 |archive-date=2020-05-18 |access-date=2020-05-17}}</ref>。

=== 專業評價 ===
{{Quote box |bgcolor=#FFFFF0 |salign=center |width=195px |align=right | quote = 「安德森先生並非現實主義者。這部電影開創了絕妙的歷史模仿，讓它的恐怖成分轉變稱一系列優雅笑話和淘氣姿態。」| source =——《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的{{tsl|en|A. O. Scott|A·O·史考特}}<ref name=Ny3 />}}

《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》進入一些影評人的前十名單<ref name="Best2014">{{Cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critic-top-10-lists-best-movies-of-2014 |title=Best of 2014: Film Critic Top Ten Lists |last=Dietz |first=Jason |date=2014-12-06 |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200317142234/https://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critic-top-10-lists-best-movies-of-2014 |archive-date=2020-03-17 |access-date=2020-03-17}}</ref>。它在2016年[[BBC|BBC]]對177名專業影評人的調查中被選為[[BBC21世紀百大電影|21世紀百大電影之一]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20160819-the-21st-centurys-100-greatest-films |title=The 21st century's 100 greatest films |date=2016-08-23 |website=BBC |access-date=2018-09-13 |archive-date=2017-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170131124228/http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20160819-the-21st-centurys-100-greatest-films |dead-url=no }}</ref>。許多評論讚賞《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》的手藝，並經常單單挑出電影的荒誕感和安德森的專業技能來作進一步讚揚<ref>{{Cite news |last=McCarthy |first=Todd |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/grand-budapest-hotel/review/677467 |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel Review |date=2014-02-06 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2014-03-16 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321225321/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/grand-budapest-hotel/review/677467 |archive-date=2014-03-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Howell |first=Peter |url=https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2014/03/13/the_grand_budapest_hotel_a_delicious_cinema_cake_review.html |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel a delicious cinema cake: Review |work=[[多倫多星報|Toronto Star]] |access-date=2014-03-16 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316052719/http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2014/03/13/the_grand_budapest_hotel_a_delicious_cinema_cake_review.html |archive-date=2014-03-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2014/03/the_grand_budapest_hotel_review_no_reservations.html |title='The Grand Budapest Hotel' review: No reservations |last=Whitty |first=Stephen |date=2014-03-07 |website=The Star-Ledger |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316051819/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2014/03/the_grand_budapest_hotel_review_no_reservations.html |archive-date=2014-03-16 |access-date=2014-03-16}}</ref>，而後者創造一個想像出來的銀幕世界，且並沒有過於認真去營造<ref name="larev">{{Cite news |last=Turan |first=Kenneth |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-grand-budapest-hotel-20140307-story.html |title=Review: Wes Anderson makes 'The Grand Budapest Hotel' a four-star delight |date=2014-03-06 |work=Los Angeles Times |access-date=2014-03-06 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307002801/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-grand-budapest-hotel-20140307,0,4029612,full.story#axzz2w5dKtMqQ |archive-date=2014-03-07 |publisher=Tribune Media}}</ref><ref name="sfrev">{{Cite news |last=LaSalle |first=Mick |url=http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Grand-Budapest-Hotel-review-Wes-Anderson-at-5314474.php |title='Grand Budapest Hotel' review: Wes Anderson at his best |date=2014-03-13 |work=[[舊金山紀事報|San Francisco Chronicle]] |access-date=2014-03-16 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316055021/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Grand-Budapest-Hotel-review-Wes-Anderson-at-5314474.php |archive-date=2014-03-16}}</ref>。《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》有時因逃避主題中某些嚴酷現實而遭到嚴厲批評。《[[名利场_(杂志)|-{zh-hans:名利场; zh-tw:浮華世界; zh-hk:名利場;}-]]》的影評人指出電影忠誠於「讓人感到有些似無重量的古怪，有時甚至霸道的俗氣冒險故事」正逐漸損害任何經認真推敲的道德教訓<ref name="vf6">{{Cite web |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/03/grand-budapest-hotel-review |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel Is a Too-Quick Trip to a Lovely Place |last=Lawson |first=Richard |date=2014-03-05 |website=Vanity Fair |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200325030624/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/03/grand-budapest-hotel-review |archive-date=2020-03-25 |access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref>。電影的優點之一是對荒唐冒險的有趣處理<ref name="Varietyreview">{{Cite news |last=Chang |first=Justin |url=https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/berlin-film-review-the-grand-budapest-hotel-1201088058/ |title=Berlin Film Review: 'The Grand Budapest Hotel' |date=2014-02-06 |work=Variety |access-date=2020-03-23 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140413133148/http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/berlin-film-review-the-grand-budapest-hotel-1201088058/ |archive-date=2014-04-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/the-grand-budapest-hotel-review-wes-andersons-best-ever-is-a-whimsical-crime-caper |title='The Grand Budapest Hotel' Review: Wes Anderson's Best Ever Is a Whimsical Crime Caper |last=Hines |first=Nico |date=2014-02-06 |website=The Daily Beast |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200324012038/https://www.thedailybeast.com/the-grand-budapest-hotel-review-wes-andersons-best-ever-is-a-whimsical-crime-caper |archive-date=2020-03-24 |access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2014/03/the-sober-frivolity-of-em-the-grand-budapest-hotel-em/284410/ |title=The Sober Frivolity of The Grand Budapest Hotel |last=Esfahani |first=Emily |date=2014-03-14 |website=The Atlantic |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315224931/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2014/03/the-sober-frivolity-of-em-the-grand-budapest-hotel-em/284410/ |archive-date=2014-03-15 |access-date=2014-03-16}}</ref>，儘管有時候一些影評人像《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》的{{tsl|en|David Denby|大衛·丹拜}}認為它的缺點是支離破碎的敘事方法似乎導致了缺乏一系列情感連貫性的事件<ref name=nyer2 />。

影評中常常提到演員的演技。記者覺得整體演員中帶有喜劇和戲劇性的時刻將《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》的價值觀帶入生活<ref name=larev /><ref name="ctrev">{{Cite news |last=Phillips |first=Michael |url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/ct-grand-budapest-hotel-20140313-column.html |title=Review: 'The Grand Budapest Hotel' |date=2014-03-13 |work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] |access-date=2020-03-23 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200324032244/https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/ct-grand-budapest-hotel-20140313-column.html |archive-date=2020-03-24}}</ref>，尤其是-{zh-hans:雷夫·范恩斯; zh-hk:賴夫·費恩斯; zh-tw:雷夫·范恩斯;}-<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20140314_Anderson_at_his_best_in__Grand_Hotel_Budapest_.html |title=Anderson at his best in 'Grand Budapest Hotel' |last=Rea |first=Steven |date=2014-03-14 |website=[[費城詢問報|The Philadelphia Inquirer]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315220310/http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20140314_Anderson_at_his_best_in__Grand_Hotel_Budapest_.html |archive-date=2014-03-15 |access-date=2014-03-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Gleiberman |first=Owen |url=https://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20483133_20764813,00.html |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel Movie Review |date=2014-03-20 |work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |access-date=2014-03-16 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318133351/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20483133_20764813,00.html |archive-date=2014-03-18}}</ref>，他的演技被稱為「讓人徹底改觀」和「簡直完美」<ref name=larev /><ref>{{Cite news |last=Neumaier |first=Joe |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/grand-budapest-hotel-movie-review-article-1.1712921 |title='The Grand Budapest Hotel': Movie review |date=2014-03-06 |work=[[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]] |access-date=2014-03-16 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309041033/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/grand-budapest-hotel-movie-review-article-1.1712921 |archive-date=2014-03-09}}</ref>。《[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]》的{{tsl|en|Mick LaSalle|米克·拉塞爾}}感覺-{zh-hans:范恩斯; zh-hk:費恩斯; zh-tw:范恩斯;}-所飾角色是一名矜持的男演員在研究如何充分展他的情感範圍<ref name=sfrev />，而《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的{{tsl|en|Kenneth Turan|肯尼斯·圖蘭}}認為他散發出一種「無限但有經過精心校準的熱忱」，也是唯一一位演員能實現安德森對「幻想世界的份量和現實（一樣的願景），同時依舊能忠實於其背後的單一精神」<ref name=larev />。另一方面，《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》的人物塑造卻得到影評人截然不同的意見，例如古斯塔夫被稱為「令人有心悅誠服感覺」和「充滿迷人般傷感」的男人<ref name=larev /><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.seattletimes.com/entertainment/movies/lsquothe-grand-budapest-hotelrsquo-itrsquos-a-trip/ |title=''The Grand Budapest Hotel'': It's a trip |last=Macdonald |first=Moira |date=2014-03-13 |website=Seattle Times |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316052354/http://seattletimes.com/html/movies/2023110356_grandbudapesthotelxml.html?syndication=rss |archive-date=2014-03-16 |access-date=2014-03-16}}</ref>，但在安德森的原則下，主角缺乏了其他立體主人翁的深度，象徵這部電影的核心角色似乎沒有完全被賦予血肉<ref name="av">{{Cite web |url=https://www.avclub.com/review/wes-anderson-erects-grand-budapest-hotel-delightfu-201851 |title=Wes Anderson erects The Grand Budapest Hotel, a delightfully madcap caper · Movie Review |last=Dowd |first=A.A. |date=2014-03-06 |website=The A.V. Club |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316064202/http://www.avclub.com/review/wes-anderson-erects-grand-budapest-hotel-delightfu-201851 |archive-date=2014-03-16 |access-date=2014-03-16}}</ref>。

[[匯總媒體|匯總媒體]][[爛番茄|爛番茄]]收集的300篇專業影評文章中，「新鮮度」為91%，平均得分8.42分（滿分10分）。網站的共識評價為「《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》一如既往的格調高雅，心思縝密到能騙到人，並再次發現魏斯·安德森使用裝飾華麗的視覺環境來表達深刻的情感想法」<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_grand_budapest_hotel |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel (2014) |website=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827234440/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_grand_budapest_hotel/ |archive-date=2019-08-27 |access-date=2020-05-17}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於48篇評論文章，平均分爲88（滿分100），代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-grand-budapest-hotel |title=The Grand Budapest Hotel (2014) |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909223145/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-grand-budapest-hotel |archive-date=2019-09-09 |access-date=2019-08-09}}</ref>。

=== 榮譽 ===
