《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》在第87屆奧斯卡金像獎賽季時並非立刻受到青睞而佔盡優勢。這部電影在3月初的開場被認為是阻止得到奧斯克認可的任何機會，因為通常按照行業規例，想獲得獎季關注的電影長片的較佳位置是排在秋季上映<ref name=varietyoscars /><ref name=Deadoscars />。上次在春季上映又取得最佳影片榮譽的只有《[[永不妥協|-{zh-hans:永不妥协;zh-hk:伊人當自強;zh-tw:永不妥協;}-]]》和《[[沉默的羔羊|沉默的羔羊]]》<ref name=Deadoscars />。隨著奧斯卡金像獎入圍名單鄰近，最有可能獲勝的電影並沒浮出水面，部分原因是評論界對這個賽季其他的強大競爭者也具有強烈反應，例如《[[美國狙擊手_(電影)|美國狙擊手]]》、《[[塞尔玛游行|-{zh-cn:塞尔玛游行;zh-tw:逐夢大道;zh-hk:馬丁·路德·金－夢想之路;}-]]》和《[[模仿游戏|-{zh-hk:解碼遊戲; zh-tw:模仿遊戲; zh-cn:模仿游戏;}-]]》<ref name="Deadoscars">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2015/01/oscars-grand-budapest-hotel-awards-1201339759/ |title=Oscars: How 'The Grand Budapest Hotel' Could Turn Awards Season On Its Head |last=Hammond |first=Pete |date=2015-01-02 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200325015244/https://deadline.com/2015/01/oscars-grand-budapest-hotel-awards-1201339759/ |archive-date=2020-03-25 |access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref>。然而，美國影評人匯編年終名單時散播他們對《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》的表彰，並因在獎項巡迴中有重要的存在感而為電影增加得獎看頭<ref name=Deadoscars />。福斯探照燈影業負責人南希·烏特利（{{lang|en|Nancy Utley}}）認為它的優勢是在多媒體家庭娛樂平台上長達數月的播放，為學院的投票人提供更多的觀看機會<ref name="varietyoscars">{{Cite news |last=Lang |first=Brent |url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/how-grand-budapest-hotel-became-a-surprise-oscars-powerhouse-1201406400/ |title=How 'Grand Budapest Hotel' Became a Surprise Oscars Powerhouse |date=2015-01-15 |work=Variety |access-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200325022104/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/how-grand-budapest-hotel-became-a-surprise-oscars-powerhouse-1201406400/ |archive-date=2020-03-25}}</ref>。它以9項提名（包括[[奧斯卡金像獎最佳影片|最佳影片]]和[[奧斯卡最佳導演獎|最佳導演]]）與《[[鳥人_(2014年電影)|-{zh-tw:鳥人; zh-cn:飞鸟侠; zh-hk:飛鳥俠;}-]]》在奧斯卡金像獎共同領跑<ref name=varietyoscars /><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-birdman-grand-budapest-hotel-764014 |title=Oscars: 'Birdman' and 'The Grand Budapest Hotel' Make a Stylish Statement |last=Kilday |first=Gregg |date=2015-01-15 |website=The Hollywood Reporter |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200325031504/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-birdman-grand-budapest-hotel-764014 |archive-date=2020-03-25 |access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref>。電影最終贏得[[奧斯卡最佳原創音樂獎|最佳原創音樂]]、[[奧斯卡最佳藝術指導獎|最佳藝術指導]]、[[奧斯卡最佳化妝與髮型設計獎|最佳化妝與髮型設計]]和[[奧斯卡最佳服裝設計獎|最佳服裝設計]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2015 |title=The 87th Academy Awards (2015) Nominees and Winners |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |access-date=2015-02-23 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223171100/http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2015 |archive-date=2015-02-23}}</ref>。

《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》因劇本、演技、執導和科技成就方面的傑出表現而在其他獎項有一席之地。它贏得[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]的{{tsl|en|Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|美國演員工會獎最佳整體演出|最佳整體演出}}和[[凯撒电影奖|-{zh-hans:凯撒电影奖;zh-hant:凱撒電影獎;zh-tw:凱薩電影獎;}-]]的{{tsl|en|César Award for Best Foreign Film|凱撒電影獎最佳外語片|最佳外語片}}<ref name=Deadoscars /><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2015/01/cesar-nominations-2015-list-cesar-award-nominees-1201361313/ |title=César Nominations: 'Saint Laurent', 'Timbuktu', Kristen Stewart In Mix – Full List |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2015-01-28 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200325034436/https://deadline.com/2015/01/cesar-nominations-2015-list-cesar-award-nominees-1201361313/ |archive-date=2020-03-25 |access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref>。電影還贏得3座[[评论家选择电影奖|评论家选择电影奖]]、5座[[英國電影學院獎|英國電影學院獎]]和[[金球獎|金球獎]][[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇電影|最佳音樂及喜劇電影]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2015/01/critics-choice-awards-winners-2015-list-movie-1201351280/ |title=Critics' Choice Awards: 'Boyhood' Wins Best Picture; 'Birdman' Leads With 7 Nods |last=Pederson |first=Erik |date=2015-01-15 |website=Deadline |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200325035446/https://deadline.com/2015/01/critics-choice-awards-winners-2015-list-movie-1201351280/ |archive-date=2020-03-25 |access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Brown |first=Mark |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/feb/08/baftas-2015-boyhood-wins-top-honours-but-grand-budapest-hotel-checks-out-with-most |title=Baftas 2015: Boyhood wins top honours but Grand Budapest Hotel checks out with most |date=2014-02-08 |work=The Guardian |access-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200325035829/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/feb/08/baftas-2015-boyhood-wins-top-honours-but-grand-budapest-hotel-checks-out-with-most |archive-date=2020-03-25 |publisher=Guardian Media Group}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-glo